graph LR;
    subgraph Server
    	A([socket]) --> B([bind])
		B --> C([listen])
		C --> D([accept])
		D --> E([recv])
		E --> F([send])
		F --> G([recv])
		G --> H([close])
    end

    subgraph Client
		I([socket]) --> J([connect])
		J --> K([send])
		K --> L([recv])
		L --> M([close])
    end

    J <--> |Establishing connection, three-way handshake|D
    K --> |Client sending data, server receiving data|E
    F --> E
    F --> |Server sending data, client reeiving data|L
    L --> K
    M --> |Client sending close message|G
